        <div class="articleTitle title"><div data-testid='title-component' class="container " data-ishtl="true">
    
    <h1>ACS-Hach Programs</h1>
    
</div></div>
    
    <div class="articleContent parsys">




    
    
    <div class="herocontainer parbase">
















<div data-testid='herocontainer-component' class="container ">
    <style type="text/css">
        #_content_acs_en_educationeducatorsacs-hach-programsjcrcontentart22571 {
        
        
        
        
        
	    
	    
        
        }
        
    </style>

    <div class="clearfix text_dark" id="_content_acs_en_educationeducatorsacs-hach-programsjcrcontentart22571">
        <div class="container">
            
            
                
                
                    <div class="containerPar parsys"><div class="columnsBootstrap parbase section">
    
    
    
    
    
    

    <div class="container " data-ishtl="true">
        
            
            <div class="row rowOdd">
                
                    <div class="col-md-8 col-xs-12 columnOne columnOdd">
                        <div class="column0 parsys">




    
    
    <div class="text parbase"><div data-testid='text-component' class="container " data-ishtl="true">
    
    
    <div>
        
        
            <h3>Over $2.5 million in scholarships and grants are awarded to 200&#43; high school chemistry teachers annually.</h3>
<p>The ACS-Hach Programs provide financial support to future and current high school chemistry teachers throughout the United States. From completing teaching credentials to obtaining support for classroom resources, chemistry teachers can count on ACS-Hach Programs to help them advance chemistry education for their students.</p>

        
    </div>
    
</div></div>


</div>
                    </div>
                
                    <div class="col-md-4 col-xs-12 columnTwo columnEven">
                        <div class="column1 parsys">




    
    
    <div class="image parbase">

<div data-testid='image-component' class="container" data-ishtl="true">
    
    
    <div id="_jcrAC_herocontainer_134702075_slash_containerPar_slash_columnsbootstrap_432_slash_column1_slash_image" class="clearfix">
        <div class="image_center  image-div">
            
            
        <div id="cq-image-jsp-/content/acs/en/education/educators/acs-hach-programs/jcr:content/articleContent/herocontainer_134702075/containerPar/columnsbootstrap_432/column1/image">
            <img alt="Science teachers speaking with students in a lab" width="522" loading="lazy" srcset="/content/acs/en/education/educators/acs-hach-programs/jcr:content/articleContent/herocontainer_134702075/containerPar/columnsbootstrap_432/column1/image.img.png/1638302443834.png 261w,
                    /content/acs/en/education/educators/acs-hach-programs/jcr:content/articleContent/herocontainer_134702075/containerPar/columnsbootstrap_432/column1/image.img.png/1638302443834.png 348w,
                    /content/acs/en/education/educators/acs-hach-programs/jcr:content/articleContent/herocontainer_134702075/containerPar/columnsbootstrap_432/column1/image.img.png/1638302443834.png 522w" sizes="(min-width: 1344px) 522px,
                    (min-width: 768px) 348px,
                    (max-width: 767px) 261px" src="/content/acs/en/education/educators/acs-hach-programs/_jcr_content/articleContent/herocontainer_134702075/containerPar/columnsbootstrap_432/column1/image.img.png/1638302443834.png"/>
            
        </div>
      

            
    <div class="image-info">
        
        
    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    
</div></div>


</div>
                    </div>
                
            </div>
            
        
        
    </div>



</div>

</div>
                
            
        </div>
    </div>

</div></div>


    
    
    <div class="herocontainer parbase">
















<div data-testid='herocontainer-component' class="container ">
    <style type="text/css">
        #_content_acs_en_educationeducatorsacs-hach-programsjcrcontentart61278 {
        
        
        
        
        
	    
	    
        
        }
        
    </style>

    <div class="clearfix text_dark" id="_content_acs_en_educationeducatorsacs-hach-programsjcrcontentart61278">
        <div class="container">
            
            
                
                
                    <div class="containerPar parsys"><div class="columnsBootstrap parbase section">
    
    
    
    
    
    

    <div class="container " data-ishtl="true">
        
            
            <div class="row rowOdd">
                
                    <div class="col-md-6 col-xs-12 columnOne columnOdd">
                        <div class="column0 parsys">




    
    
    <div class="text parbase"><div data-testid='text-component' class="container " data-ishtl="true">
    
    
    <div>
        
        
            <h2>Scholarships</h2>
<p><b>For Future High School Chemistry Teachers</b></p>

        
    </div>
    
</div></div>


    
    
    <div class="acscontainer parbase">
    

    
    <div class="clearfix box-style1" data-testid='acscontainer-component' data-ishtl="true">
        <span class="media-label"></span>
        
        
            <div class="containerPar parsys"><div class="text parbase section"><div data-testid='text-component' class="container " data-ishtl="true">
    
    
    <div>
        
        
            <h4> </h4>
<h4><a href="/funding/scholarships-fellowships/acs-hach-post-baccalaureate-teacher-scholarship.html">ACS-Hach Post-Baccalaureate Teacher Scholarship</a></h4>
<p>Awarded to recent graduates and graduate students with limited work experience and an interest in becoming secondary chemistry teachers. <b>Applications are now be accepted through May 1, 2024. </b></p>

        
    </div>
    
</div></div>

</div>
        
    </div>
    
</div>


    
    
    <div class="acscontainer parbase">
    

    
    <div class="clearfix box-style1" data-testid='acscontainer-component' data-ishtl="true">
        <span class="media-label"></span>
        
        
            <div class="containerPar parsys"><div class="text parbase section"><div data-testid='text-component' class="container " data-ishtl="true">
    
    
    <div>
        
        
            <h4> </h4>
<h4><b><a href="/funding/scholarships-fellowships/acs-hach-second-career-teacher-scholarship.html">ACS-Hach Second Career Teacher Scholarship</a></b></h4>
<p>Provides financial support for chemistry professionals to obtain a masters degree in education or teacher certification in chemistry.  <b>Applications are now be accepted through May 1, 2024.</b></p>

        
    </div>
    
</div></div>

</div>
        
    </div>
    
</div>


    
    
    <div class="acscontainer parbase">
    

    
    <div class="clearfix box-style1" data-testid='acscontainer-component' data-ishtl="true">
        <span class="media-label"></span>
        
        
            <div class="containerPar parsys"><div class="text parbase section"><div data-testid='text-component' class="container " data-ishtl="true">
    
    
    <div>
        
        
            <h4> </h4>
<h4><b><a href="/funding/scholarships-fellowships/acs-hach-land-grant-undergraduate-scholarship.html">ACS-Hach Land Grant Undergraduate Scholarship</a></b></h4>
<p>Provides financial support to obtain a chemistry undergraduate degree and chemistry teaching credentials at one of our 72 partner institutions.</p>

        
    </div>
    
</div></div>

</div>
        
    </div>
    
</div>


</div>
                    </div>
                
                    <div class="col-md-6 col-xs-12 columnTwo columnEven">
                        <div class="column1 parsys">




    
    
    <div class="text parbase"><div data-testid='text-component' class="container " data-ishtl="true">
    
    
    <div>
        
        
            <h2>Grants</h2>
<p><b>For Current High School Chemistry Teachers</b></p>

        
    </div>
    
</div></div>


    
    
    <div class="acscontainer parbase">
    

    
    <div class="clearfix box-style1" data-testid='acscontainer-component' data-ishtl="true">
        <span class="media-label"></span>
        
        
            <div class="containerPar parsys"><div class="text parbase section"><div data-testid='text-component' class="container " data-ishtl="true">
    
    
    <div>
        
        
            <h4> </h4>
<h4><b><a href="/funding/grants/acs-hach-high-school-chemistry-classroom-grant.html">ACS-Hach High School Chemistry Classroom Grant</a></b></h4>
<p>Funds resources, activities, and laboratory equipment for the high school chemistry classroom. <b>Applications are now be accepted through June 1, 2024.</b></p>

        
    </div>
    
</div></div>

</div>
        
    </div>
    
</div>


    
    
    <div class="acscontainer parbase">
    

    
    <div class="clearfix box-style1" data-testid='acscontainer-component' data-ishtl="true">
        <span class="media-label"></span>
        
        
            <div class="containerPar parsys"><div class="text parbase section"><div data-testid='text-component' class="container " data-ishtl="true">
    
    
    <div>
        
        
            <h4> </h4>
<h4><b><a href="/funding/grants/acs-hach-professional-development-grant.html">ACS-Hach Professional Development Grant</a></b></h4>
<p>Funds professional development experiences for secondary chemistry teachers.  </p>

        
    </div>
    
</div></div>

</div>
        
    </div>
    
